BlackJack_Commands.name: $play21 start
BlackJack_Commands.description: Starts the black jack game. All players automatically draw 2 cards.

BlackJack_Commands.name: $play21 hit
BlackJack_Commands.description: Adds a card to the player who called this command.

BlackJack_Commands.name: $play21 compare
BlackJack_Commands.description: Compares all player cards values. Who ever has the highest value under 21 wins. Players automatically draw 2 cards.

BlackJack_Commands.name: $play21 info
BlackJack_Commands.description: Displays all command information and game rules.
